rows.label: qev002201_MSG0005
rows.name:
My work as director general can truly begin once
peace is finally upon us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev002201_MSG0006
rows.name:
I promise to transform our New LA into a city every bit
as impressive as the Los Angeles of old.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev002201_MSG0007
rows.name:
But we're not there yet, so I'm counting on you
BLADE operatives to lend us your talents for a little
while longer.[ST:wait ]
